See the end of the file for license conditions.
----------------------------------------------------------------
This is the simplest JPEG network streamer that you can think about. It is even dumb, but may be useful some of you out there.

The package contains two executables, one for v4l version 1 and the other for v4l version 2. Chose the one you need depending on the hardware available.

Notes:
The v4l2 server expects a device delivering YUYV image format. This is hard-coded and you will need



